### Hadith 2:698

*Narrated Um Salama:*

I informed Allah's Apostle that I was sick. He said, "Perform Tawaf (of
the Kaba) while riding behind the people." So, I performed the Tawaf
while Allah's Apostle was offering the prayer beside the Kaba and was
reciting Surat-at-Tur.

